divs: Sighting Detailsi was outside with my dog.and i have always looked up into the sky.i have a teloscope.it was around 9pm and this object came right over the house.iit was boomerang shape,no sound and what i thought were 4 lights underneath,but on thinking for the passed year i would say it was the crafts power.i couldnt say how far up it was but it was low enuff to see the shape.as soon as i seen it i knew it wasnt anything from this world.any aircraft i have ever seen always makes a sound,some louder than others.my feelings were,i finally seen a ufo.told my wife and family.dont think they believed me.but i know what i seen and didnt hear.
Summary: i was outside with my dog and the ufo passed overhead.
